I have problems to use the GUI (Update Creation Wizard) for the custom rules. I need rules to publish the updates on only needes workstations.<br />
<br />
A test installation on Mictosoft Windows 2003R2 / WSUS 3.0 SP2 (the same as my production environment) let me publish some software (for example: Adobe AIR)<br />
<br />
i have problems to use the gui, so i export some rules and edit the ASCII File. Fine, that works fine. Now i want to publish the latest update from AIR, and a new rule does not work. If i load the rule, a messagebox with no content appears<br />
<pre><code>&lt;lar:And&gt;
&lt;lar:Or&gt;
  &lt;bar:WindowsVersion Comparison=&quot;GreaterThanOrEqualTo&quot; MajorVersion=&quot;6&quot; MinorVersion=&quot;1&quot; ProductType=&quot;1&quot;/&gt;
&lt;/lar:Or&gt;
&lt;lar:Or&gt;
  &lt;bar:Processor Architecture=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;
  &lt;bar:Processor Architecture=&quot;9&quot;/&gt;
